parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden deployment of the active headrest can cause injury or distraction to the driver, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The headrest deploys unexpectedly
hitting the back of the head or neck
sometimes causing injury or fear of injury.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag and Seat Belt Pretensioner Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and seat belt pretensioner can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light is on
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
or the seat belt pretensioner fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or failure to repair the Takata airbag recall can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light is on
the recall repair is delayed or unavailable
or the dealer is unable to complete the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and loss of power can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls
loses power
and may not restart immediately; warning lights such as the check engine light
traction control light
and electronic throttle control light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause safety risks, such as loss of power, unexpected starting, and unexpected locking of doors, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle may start unexpectedly
doors may lock or unlock unexpectedly
windows may roll up or down unexpectedly
and warning lights such as the electronic throttle control light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle Body and Electronic Throttle Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Throttle body and electronic throttle control issues can cause loss of power, stalling, and unexpected acceleration, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may lose power
stall
or accelerate unexpectedly; warning lights such as the electronic throttle control light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Anti-lock Brake System (ABS) and Traction Control Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS and traction control issues can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle may lose traction
ABS warning light may illuminate
and traction control warning light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: TPMS issues can cause tire failure, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The TPMS warning light may illuminate
and the tire pressure may be low.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fire hazard can cause injuries, fatalities, and property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle may catch fire
and electrical system failures may occur.
